{"id":265610,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/奇闻录-算算周口平坟的那些帐/","date":"2012-11-28T05:00:24Z","modified":"2012-11-28T05:00:24Z","title":"奇闻录 | 算算周口平坟的那些帐","content":"<p><p>河南周口今年开展了大规模“平坟复耕”运动。截止目前，已平坟200多万座，复耕3万亩。是什么让当地政府罔顾民怨强制推行这项运动？腾讯新闻百科特别制作了一张信息图示，告诉你周口平坟运动能够给政府带来多少收入。<span></span></p>\n<p>此外，附上一则关于周口平坟运动的报道：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://qiwen.lu/uploads/henan-pingfen-diaocha.pdf\">《河南运动式「平坟」调查》</a>（作者：余声）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://qiwen.lu/wp-content/uploads/zhoukoupingfen.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"460\" height=\"2866\" /></p>\n<p>来源：<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.qq.com/newspedia/93.htm\">腾讯新闻百科</a></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?i=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?a=UTC8GdS0vbg:OmIF3oyJOM4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/qi-wen-lu?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/qi-wen-lu/~4/UTC8GdS0vbg\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae